&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equal Opportunity &amp;amp; Affirmative Action:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ABI Growth&amp;nbsp;Group is proud to be an Equal Opportunity and Affirmative Action employer. We do not discriminate based upon of race, color, national origin, gender, gender identity, sexual orientation, protected veteran status, disability, age, or other applicable legally protected characteristics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following fields are optional, but anticipate the information for your registration*.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remember: your data will never be used as elimination criteria in selection processes. With them, ABI Growth&amp;nbsp;Group is able to analyze diversity and reduce biases in selection processes. We want to contribute to changing this reality by being an inclusive company.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;For more information: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bees.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;www.bees.com&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.abinbev.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;www.abinbev.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About BEES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Join us to build the future of B2B commerce!&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;BEES is AB InBev’s B2B platform. Through our ecosystem,&amp;nbsp;merchants&amp;nbsp;and retailers across 29 countries can stock their businesses quickly, easily, and securely.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;At BEES, we dream big, lead with purpose, and develop technology that transforms the way retailers and sellers grow.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Every line of code and every partnership is built in service of a single mission: to make commerce better for retailers and sellers around the world. Here, your work is not&amp;nbsp;just important. It makes a difference!&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About this opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;261&quot; data-end=&quot;484&quot;&gt;Do you enjoy solving complex problems through data and want to help shape the future of the BEES Marketplace? This opportunity is for professionals who are passionate about analytics, customer data, and AI-driven solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;486&quot; data-end=&quot;876&quot;&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll partner closely with Marketplace, Product, Personalization, and Data teams to improve how we identify, consolidate, and enrich customer information across the BEES ecosystem. You&#39;ll play a key role in developing customer identity algorithms, improving account governance, identifying buyer growth opportunities, and supporting a secure, scalable Marketplace experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What you will do:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;deczh9&quot; data-start=&quot;901&quot; data-end=&quot;1024&quot;&gt;Lead customer identity and account consolidation initiatives, creating a unified customer view across the BEES ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;xbgsu6&quot; data-start=&quot;1025&quot; data-end=&quot;1138&quot;&gt;Partner with Product, Data, and Personalization teams to improve customer matching algorithms and &lt;em class=&quot;Highlight ht57699da5-383a-4938-8cdf-1c542cae5e81&quot;&gt;data quality&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1h6b4dy&quot; data-start=&quot;1139&quot; data-end=&quot;1239&quot;&gt;Drive customer data enrichment initiatives to ensure reliable and actionable customer information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1o3pl1n&quot; data-start=&quot;1240&quot; data-end=&quot;1346&quot;&gt;Identify opportunities to expand the Marketplace buyer base through data analysis and business insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;cfgc88&quot; data-start=&quot;1347&quot; data-end=&quot;1435&quot;&gt;Support user governance and fraud prevention initiatives, ensuring a trusted platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1yzggys&quot; data-start=&quot;1436&quot; data-end=&quot;1532&quot;&gt;Collaborate with regional stakeholders, including teams in Mexico, on Marketplace initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
