&lt;p&gt;We are looking for passionate, curious, and driven student to join the &lt;strong&gt;BEES Internship&lt;/strong&gt;. As an intern, you will have the opportunity to contribute to high-impact projects, gain hands-on experience in a global tech-driven organization, and learn directly from experts in product, operations, technology, and digital transformation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Technical Customer Success team&lt;/strong&gt; is focused on understanding and supporting consumer and customer needs, harnessing new technology, and scaling growth opportunities. They are implementing BEES systems with strategic partner companies across LATAM.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll need:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently pursuing a degree in &lt;strong&gt;Technology, Engineering, Business Administration, Marketing, or related fields&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expected graduation: &lt;strong&gt;December 2027 to July 2028&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced English&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability to work &lt;strong&gt;on-site in São Paulo starting in August 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for someone who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has a strong interest in solving real business problems and enjoys learning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is proactive, communicative, and comfortable collaborating in a team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is passionate about &lt;strong&gt;technology, product management, data, and digital transformation&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is interested in working with &lt;strong&gt;Excel and Power BI.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location: &lt;strong&gt;BEES Office – São Paulo (on-site)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
