&lt;li&gt;Develop methodologies to estimate market potential and identify market share growth opportunities across countries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain prioritization frameworks to identify the most strategic customers for commercial expansion and competitive growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead initiatives to identify, segment, and develop high-impact customers, creating scalable approaches that can be replicated across markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, execute, and monitor personalized commercial activations that drive customer acquisition, market share growth, and brand-building objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze competitive landscapes and support country teams with data-driven strategies to increase market penetration and win share from competitors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor business KPIs and collaborate closely with Product, Data, and Country teams to maximize commercial impact through analytics and experimentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
