&lt;li&gt;Map and define country-specific delivery processes and identify how BEES Deliver should be integrated into those operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and prioritize Business Unit requirements in partnership with the digital product team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the ideation and development of capabilities required to align the digital product with Business Unit operational processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the subject matter expert for BEES Deliver, providing guidance and support to Business Units on product functionality and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
