&lt;p&gt;Join us to build the future of B2B commerce!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BEES is AB InBev’s B2B platform. Through our ecosystem, merchants and retailers across 29 countries can stock their businesses quickly, easily, and securely. At BEES, we dream big, lead with purpose, and develop technology that transforms the way retailers and sellers grow.&lt;/p&gt;
