&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About BEES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to build the future of B2B commerce!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BEES is AB InBev’s B2B platform. Through our ecosystem, merchants and retailers across 29 countries can stock their businesses quickly, easily, and securely. At BEES, we dream big, lead with purpose, and develop technology that transforms the way retailers and sellers grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every line of code and every partnership is built in service of a single mission: to make commerce better for retailers and sellers around the world. Here, your work is not just important. It makes a difference!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, and maintain scalable backend services using Java and Spring Boot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the evolution of microservices architecture, ensuring performance, resilience, and maintainability;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and optimize RESTful APIs and integrations across distributed systems;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve system observability, monitoring, and logging;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver scalable solutions aligned with business needs;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in technical discussions, architecture decisions, and continuous improvement initiatives;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow engineering best practices, including code quality, testing, and automation;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to CI/CD pipelines, deployment processes, and cloud-native environments;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support containerized applications using technologies such as Docker and Kubernetes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for people with:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;University degree in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Information Systems, Systems Analysis and Development, or related fields;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid backend development experience with Java;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and maintaining RESTful APIs and microservices;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing and scaling high-throughput and distributed applications;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with application monitoring and observability tools such as New Relic, Datadog, or similar platforms;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with DevOps and cloud-native tools such as Docker, Kubernetes, Azure, or similar technologies;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in Agile environments;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong fundamentals in object-oriented design, data structures, algorithms, and problem solving;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with Spring Framework technologies such as Spring Boot, Spring Security, and Spring MVC;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of design patterns, software architecture, and development best practices;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with software testing concepts, including unit, integration, regression, stress, and test automation;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intermediate English communication skills, both written and spoken.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
